  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>一人分しかないこの解毒剤は
僕達がもらっていく</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We'll be taking this antidote,
and there's only enough for one person.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>はぁ？　ふざけんなよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? Don't mess around like that!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ふざけんなよって膝蹴んなよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't make a mess messing around!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>The joke here is fuzaken sounding like hizaken. Fuzaken is like, don't mess around. Hizaken is a knee strike. I wasn't sure hwo to incorporate both of these.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>これは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>This is...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クレスのハチマキをクレッス！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Cless' headband's name is Cless!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>No idea what to do with this one.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>僕には……解毒剤が必要なんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I have... need of that antidote.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リオンの恩返し！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Leon's repaying a favor!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>I'm not sure if this is meant to be a pun? It doesn't seem like it.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Problematic</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>なるほどな。
だが、こっちも譲れねぇんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I see.
But I'm not calling it quits either!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
